{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, Liu et al. (2022) presented a virtual assistant for online courses to resolve general and repetitive doubts about content and teaching materials.",
    "This system incorporates a sentiment analysis module to analyze the response's satisfaction based on the student's dialogue.",
    "They used two fine-tuning versions of BERT model with an accuracy of 82% and 90% for the correct detection of the content and student's sentiment, respectively.",
    "Moreover, Mahajan (2022) created a system for students to improve their knowledge of the English language that allows them to obtain information on the meaning of words, make translations, and resolve pronunciation doubts.",
    "The authors exploited the RoBERTa model with an accuracy greater than 98% in communication intent detection."
  ]
}